    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Anxiety</strong>: Learn how <a href="https://elemental.medium.com/how-anxiety-fuels-your-anxiety-27a4d4b15277" target="_self">anxiety fuels anxiety</a>.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Stress</strong>: Read <a href="https://medium.com/how-a-stress-expert-deals-with-her-own-stress-48d78b1f562" target="_self">how a stress expert deals with her own stress</a>.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Depression</strong>: See my 4-part series on <a href="https://elemental.medium.com/can-we-prevent-depression-ec25706406b7" target="_self">depression prevention</a>, <a href="https://elemental.medium.com/its-time-to-really-talk-about-depression-d674a72219da" target="_self">stigma</a>, <a href="https://elemental.medium.com/the-real-problem-with-antidepressants-898e83133bbc" target="_self">the problem with meds</a>, and <a href="https://elemental.medium.com/why-depression-so-often-goes-untreated-c481a4c420fe" target="_self">why depression so often is not treated</a>.</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
